<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10130818>
    dc:description "Fig. 12. Distributions of Phlaeopterus species based on all georeferenced specimen records. A) P. loganensis, B) P. longipennis. Grey dots represent localities where at least one Phlaeopterus species, but not the species of interest, was collected. Red dots represent localities where the species of interest was collected." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10130818/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10130869>
    dc:description "Fig. 36. Phlaeopterus species, eyes, dorsal view. A) P. lagrandeuri, B) P. houkae, C) P. longipennis, D) P. frosti, E) P. bakerensis, F) P. olympicus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10130869/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10130861>
    dc:description "Fig. 32. Maxillary palpi of A) Lesteva pallipes, B) Unamis sp. undescribed, C) Phlaeopterus longipennis, D) Phlaeopterus bakerensis. Labial palpi of E) Unamis sp., F) Phlaeopterus cavicollis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10130861/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10130881>
    dc:description "Fig. 42. Heads, ventral view, of A) Unamis sp. undescribed, B) Unamis sp., C) Phlaeopterus lagrandeuri, D) Phlaeopterus houkae, E) Phlaeopterus longipennis, F) Phlaeopterus elongatus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10130881/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10130824>
    dc:description "Fig. 15. Pronota, dorsal view, of A) Lesteva pallipes LeConte, 1863, B) Lesteva longoelytrata (Goeze, 1777), C) Unamis sp. undescribed, D) Unamis sp., E) Phlaeopterus lagrandeuri, F) Phlaeopterus houkae, G) Phlaeopterus longipennis, H) Phlaeopterus obsoletus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10130824/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10130832>
    dc:description "Fig. 20. Phlaeopterus species, mesosterna, ventral oblique view. A) P. longipennis, B) P. obsoletus, C) P. olympicus, D) P. frosti, E) P. occidentalis, F) P. elongatus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10130832/files/figure.png" ;
